main event: A UFO sighting was reported in Asbury Park, New Jersey, on November 23, 1957, involving an unidentified object moving irregularly against the wind.
interesting points: The object was described as a white object appearing to travel at a good speed, It exhibited a brilliant green color at times, The sighting lasted for approximately 20 minutes, The object moved in a southeast direction while initially spotted in the northwest, There was insufficient data for evaluation regarding the nature of the object.
witness description: Observers located in one of the most heavily travelled airways.
